name: It's a Trap! - Gamma World 7E theme
description: # It's A Trap! - Gamma World 7E theme_v3.0 updates:_* Updated the trap theme to be compatible with It's A Trap v3.0.This is a trap theme to support the Gamma World 7E character sheet.To use this theme for the It's A Trap! script, enter 'GammaWorld7' for the ```theme``` user option.
